o games are still hot, but early shoppers are snapping up traditional dolls and toys. |website= [[Los Angeles Times]] |date=June 28, 1989 |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-11-24-vw-231-story.html |accessdate=August 26, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826210242/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-11-24-vw-231-story.html |archivedate=August 26, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LATimesVideo1\">{{cite web|first=Dennis |last=Hunt|title =Video Rental Charts |website= [[Los Angeles Times]] |date=December 28, 1989 |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-12-28-ca-1691-story.html |accessdate=August 26, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826204508/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-12-28-ca-1691-story.html|archivedate=August 26, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LATImesVideo2\">{{cite web| title =Video Rental Charts : 'Working Girl' No Match For 'Batman' |website= [[Los Angeles Times]] |date=December 28, 1989 |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-12-07-ca-444-story.html |accessdate=August 26, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826204700/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-12-07-ca-444-story.html |archivedate=August 26, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LocationMuseum\">{{cite web|first=Daniel |last=Crudge| title =Ghostbusters: The Ultimate Film Location Guide |website= [[Expedia|Expedia.com]] |date=March 11, 2016 |url=https://www.expedia.co.uk/explore/ghostbusters-the-ultimate-film-location-guide |accessdate=August 26, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616190141/https://www.expedia.co.uk/explore/ghostbusters-the-ultimate-film-location-guide |archivedate=June 16, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MashableChatter\">{{cite web|first=Pramit |last=Chatterjee |title=Even After 30 Years, \u2018Ghostbusters 2\u2019 Continues To Be a Slime River Of Social And Political Relevance |url=https://in.mashable.com/entert