ana-jones-ghostbusters-lead-a-sequel-heavy-1989/ |website=[[Uproxx|Uproxx.com]] |date=April 30, 2014 |accessdate=August 22, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822182627/https://uproxx.com/hitfix/summer-movies-flashback-batman-indiana-jones-ghostbusters-lead-a-sequel-heavy-1989/  |archivedate=August 22, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"VanityFair2014\">{{cite web|last=Blume| first=Lesley M. M. | url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/ghostbusters-making-of| title=The Making of Ghostbusters: How Dan Aykroyd, Harold Ramis, and \"The Murricane\" Built \"The Perfect Comedy\"| website=[[Vanity Fair (magazine)|Vanity Fair]] |  date=June 4, 2014| accessdate=December 20, 2018| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180317063300/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/ghostbusters-making-of| archivedate=March 17, 2018| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ViceVideoGames\">{{cite web| last=Diver | first=Mike | url=https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/3bjwkn/a-brief-history-of-ghostbusters-and-video-games-250 | title=A Brief History of Ghostbusters and Video Games | website=[[Vice (magazine)|Vice]] | date=February 4, 2016 | accessdate=December 20, 2018| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608181159/https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/3bjwkn/a-brief-history-of-ghostbusters-and-video-games-250 | archivedate=June 8, 2019 | url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"VultureControl\">{{cite web |first=Jada |last=Yuan |title=Ivan Reitman on Bill Murray, Internet Trolls, and Why He Fought for the Ghostbusters Reboot |url=https://www.vulture.com/2016/07/ivan-reitman-ghostbusters-bill-murray-qa.html | website=[[New York (magazine)|Vulture]] |date=July 14, 2016 |accessdate=September 7, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608084559/https://www.vulture.com/2016/07/ivan-reitman-ghostbusters-bill-murray-qa.html |archivedate=June 8, 2019|url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"VultureAug14\">{{cite web |first=Brian |last=Feldman |t