ol|Bristol, United Kingdom]] |url=https://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/intellect/ajpc/2015/00000004/00000001/art00003 }}\n*{{cite journal | ref=harv| last=Corcos |first=Christine Alice |title=\"Who Ya Gonna C(S)ite?\" Ghostbusters and the Environmental Regulation Debate |year=1997 |isbn= |publisher=[[Paul M. Hebert Law Center|Louisiana State University Law Center]] |journal=Florida State University Journal of Land Use and Environmental Law |volume= 13 |issue= 1 |location=[[Baton Rouge, Louisiana]] |url=https://ir.law.fsu.edu/jluel/vol13/iss1/6/ }}\n* {{cite magazine|last=Eisenberg |first=Adam |title=Ghostbusters II: Ghostbusters Revisited |magazine=[[Cinefex]]|publisher=  |publication-place=  |location=[[United States]]  |issue=40 |date=November 1989 |page= |url=https://cinefex.com/backissues/issue40.htm |accessdate=September 3, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831135218/https://www.theraffon.net/~spookcentral/gb2_book_cinefex40.pdf |archivedate=August 31, 2019 |url-status=live |isbn= |issn=0198-1056 |oclc= |ref=harv }}\n* {{cite news |last=Groen |first=Rick|date=June 19, 1989 |title=Film Review Ghostbusters II |work=[[The Globe and Mail]] |publisher=The Woodbridge Company |location=[[United States]] |page= D9 |url= |accessdate= |isbn= |issn= |oclc= |ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book | ref=harv| last=Matthews |first=Nicole |title=Comic Politics: Gender in Hollywood Comedy After the New Right  |year=2000  |isbn= |publisher=[[Manchester University Press]] |location=[[Manchester|Manchester, England]] |url=https://books.google.co.in/books?id=oSDgMnlWln4C&pg=PA106#v=onepage&q&f=true }}\n* {{cite magazine| ref=harv| last=McCabe| first=Joseph |year= 2016 |title=Bustin' Out a Sequel | magazine=[[SFX (magazine)|The Complete SFX Guide to Ghostbusters]] |publisher=[[Future plc]]  |location=[[United Kingdom]] |url=https://archive.org/details/SFX.Special.Edition.The.Complete.Guide.to.Ghostbusters.2016.True.PDF/page/n55 |accessdate=August 29, 2019 |isbn=}}\n* {{cite mag