 Of Ghostbusters |url=https://www.stereogum.com/1885140/something-weird-indeed-the-music-of-ghostbusters/franchises/sounding-board/ |website=[[Stereogum]] |date=June 30, 2016 |accessdate=September 6, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524014332/https://www.stereogum.com/1885140/something-weird-indeed-the-music-of-ghostbusters/franchises/sounding-board/ |archivedate=May 24, 2019  |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SyFyApr19\">{{cite web |first=Jeff |last=Spry |title=Sony's New Ghostbusters 4K Blu-Ray Steelbook Release Is Packed With Rare And Never-Seen Extras |url=https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/sonys-new-ghostbusters-4k-blu-ray-steelbook-release-is-packed-with-rare-and-never-seen |website=[[Syfy|Syfy.com]] |date=April 7, 2019 |accessdate=June 30, 2019 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190630171757/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/sonys-new-ghostbusters-4k-blu-ray-steelbook-release-is-packed-with-rare-and-never-seen |archivedate=June 30, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"TestedMay15\">{{cite web |first=David |last=Konow |title=Putting Together ''Ghostbusters''{{'}} Special Effects |url=https://www.tested.com/art/movies/524482-putting-together-ghostbusters-special-effects/ |website=[[Tested.com]] |date=May 7, 2015 |accessdate=June 22, 2019 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190622222404/https://www.tested.com/art/movies/524482-putting-together-ghostbusters-special-effects/ |archivedate=June 22, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"THRApr16\">{{cite web|first=Graeme |last=McMillan | title=Remembering the Long Forgotten 'Ghostbusters' Spinoffs Through the Years | url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ghostbusters-spinoffs-a-brief-history-888253 | date=April 27, 2016 | website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]| accessdate=August 5, 2019 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527215814/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ghostbusters-spinoffs-a-brief-history-888253 |archivedate=May 27, 2016 |url-status=live}}</